381	4	94	To comply with data protection regulations such as GDPR and CCPA, organizations must implement robust encryption, access controls, and data masking techniques for AI workloads, both at rest and in transit. Emerging AI capabilities necessitate considerations for an AI Bill of Rights.  Data privacy: Data governance models and tools like Watson Knowledge Catalog are essential for ensuring the privacy of individuals' data. Differential privacy offers a mathematical algorithm to prevent an individual or organization from identifying an individual within a protected dataset through comparison of the data to other data sets. IBM Z Data Privacy Passports provide comprehensive data protection solutions.	[-0.10747903,0.03512897,-0.021196716,0.021372143,0.01091602,0.02514338,0.0069066496,-0.036227535,-0.00085728214,-0.012164676,0.013912256,0.011967724,0.079258464,-0.00044654522,-0.0020747653,0.0033054494,0.026941884,-0.0026091167,-0.06854664,-0.06190728,-0.01548618,0.05558268,-0.03051166,-0.001018535,-0.034358885,0.04531382,0.09140835,-0.08551953,-0.0036142447,-0.00915349,0.036258772,-0.075577475,0.04083372,0.07221586,-0.0036639182,-0.06764621,0.010537891,0.016014015,0.044253305,-0.038923055,-0.068036415,-0.09224218,-0.06307472,-0.02788387,0.011122142,0.09999007,0.014143671,-0.017078267,-0.045240656,0.017812066,-0.04342073,-0.024370696,-0.008098355,0.046980757,-0.028149342,-0.0038171376,-0.07395364,-0.04915061,-0.030362187,-0.003338775,-0.06540448,-0.04197766,0.049318176,0.050403573,0.030076379,0.08312626,-0.064566135,-0.00074781483,-0.00967963,-0.052484926,-0.016877078,0.056166433,-0.03574284,0.030055901,0.016945478,-0.014966697,-0.015184485,-0.04622532,0.047119316,-0.06556152,-0.009073248,0.021750093,0.0438362,0.10950013,-0.004185286,0.0039242133,-0.013709195,-0.002722281,0.012941879,0.024439847,0.040563308,-0.024598131,0.0853917,0.008451814,-0.013209401,-0.03053912,-0.02088726,0.008894154,-0.0017364675,-0.007915136,-0.033357415,0.04908643,0.012970159,0.0057483166,0