 ensures the safety, reliability, and security of autonomous vehicle operations.  Agriculture IBM Z can assist in managing data from various sensors and cameras used to monitor crop health, assess yields, and automate agricultural processes. It can process this data to optimize irrigation, fertilization, and harvesting.  Optical character recognition (OCR) IBM Z can provide the computing power needed for OCR applications. It can handle the processing of large volumes of scanned documents and images, converting text into machine-readable data for various purposes like document management and data extraction.	[-0.058453765,0.026884656,-0.050571013,-0.095841885,0.04825499,-0.031906493,0.06572808,0.048935276,-0.002565619,-0.011482413,-0.04555064,0.039723717,0.04521612,0.038589675,-0.026821816,0.006454929,0.07068613,-0.028942585,-0.071087115,-0.036784105,0.003319213,-0.063600615,-0.0049233665,-0.050089855,-0.051778335,0.031743903,0.033075098,-0.046493504,-0.002109481,-0.029642187,-0.0097284615,-0.0010034203,0.07172775,0.095048964,-0.031968217,-0.053329926,0.11397773,-0.06053265,-0.05912955,-0.08008421,-0.024514433,0.008553789,-0.05394179,0.015861584,0.061078396,0.060007356,0.0014625523,-0.08136986,0.023860795,-0.022046667,-0.14711128,-0.064011574,0.043234866,0.061620418,-0.1201175,0.07969254,-0.017422229,-0.038205888,-0.0013149476,-0.0015368923,-0.0204042,-0.017566914,0.038776495,0.07377675,0.007196001,0.07055495,-0.026229082,-0.06606398,0.025511973,-0.082736336,-0.0642665,0.009451822,0.0012254937,0.053835552,-0.18181229,-0.01703007,0.086937286,-0.13231026,0.031417504,-0.098929815,0.039649602,0.038827706,-0.040653855,0.051670127,0.054148335,0.054546956,-0.06898313,0.03769164,-0.014441635,-0.014712284,0.021745522,0.006664151,-0.004744662,-0.05455831,-0.0069711553,-0.064080715,0.042143106,-0.050138127,0.033059604,0.013993345,0.01699873,0.0043802178,0.1593328,-0.017406788,-0.013030612,-0.028054545,0.057698224,0.011368561,-0.049936235,0.064461865,-0.043140937,-0.024098812,-0